        <title>如何快速给PDF添加书签</title>
        <link>https://monoshy.github.io/p/%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E5%BF%AB%E9%80%9F%E7%BB%99pdf%E6%B7%BB%E5%8A%A0%E4%B9%A6%E7%AD%BE/</link>
